@startuml
title Connectivity Monitoring

actor Operator
participant Frontend
participant "Control Plane API" as API
participant "Health Engine" as Health
participant "Probe Runners" as Probe
participant "Stream Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Perception Service" as Perception
database "Metadata Store" as Metadata
participant "Metrics Scraper" as Scraper

loop Scheduled probe cycle
  Health -> Metadata: Load active camera topology
  loop Per camera source
    Health -> Probe: request source probe
    Probe --> Health: ProbeSample
  end
  Health -> Gateway: Read stream session metrics
  Gateway --> Health: Stream metrics
  Health -> Perception: Read observation freshness
  Perception --> Health: Observation freshness
  Health -> Health: Compute logical health snapshot
  Health -> Metadata: Persist HealthSnapshot
end

Operator -> Frontend: Open monitoring tab
Frontend -> API: GET monitoring snapshot
API -> Metadata: Read latest HealthSnapshot
Metadata --> API: Current snapshot
API --> Frontend: Camera and source health snapshot

Scraper -> API: GET /metrics
API -> Metadata: Read current snapshot and metric summaries
API --> Scraper: Prometheus-style metrics

opt Force manual probe
  Operator -> Frontend: Click "Probe now"
  Frontend -> API: POST force probe
  API -> Health: Run immediate probe
  Health -> Metadata: Persist fresh snapshot
  API --> Frontend: Fresh snapshot
end

@enduml
